# data/dedup_index.csv and data/normalized/permits_normalized.csv are
# intentionally TRACKED (not ignored): GitHub Actions runners are
# stateless between runs, so this repo is the only persistence layer for
# "what have we already seen" across days. The daily workflow commits
# updates to these two files back to the repo. See core/rollup.py and
# .github/workflows/daily_permit_collection.yml.
